What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Ophthalmic Surgical Instruments Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Global Ophthalmic Surgical Instruments Market

Ophthalmic surgical instruments market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the ophthalmic surgical instruments market to account grow at a CAGR of 10.1% in the above-mentioned forecast period. Increasing awareness of ophthalmic surgical instruments among the population has been directly impacting the growth of ophthalmic surgical instruments market.

The ophthalmic devices are used in the diagnosis and treatment of eyes associated diseases such as peripheral vitreoretinal disease, vision loss due to aging, refractive eye state, glaucoma treatment, cataract surgeries, and others in hospitals or other specialty clinics. The rising number of players to develop and launch ophthalmic devices for further enhancement such as clear visualization by using ophthalmic microscopes, smartphone associated ophthalmic devices, and devices being used for glaucoma and cataract surgeries.

Growth in the aging population and increasing prevalence of chronic disorders such as diabetes and hypertension is the main driving factor for the ophthalmic surgical instruments market. Increase the demand for ophthalmic equipment across the globe due to demand for the accurate treatment of diseases is driving the market. A number of age-related macular degeneration (AMD) cases is on the rise with the growing prevalence of diabetes which is an opportunity for the ophthalmic surgical instruments market. A huge population base in developing countries across the world is also an opportunity for the ophthalmic surgical instruments market.

Lack of awareness and low access to eye care in low-income economies is a big challenge for the ophthalmic surgical instruments market. However, high costs of ophthalmology devices are the main restraint in the growth of ophthalmic surgical instruments market during the forecast period of 2021-2028.

